# ChangeLog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](http://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/)
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](http://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [2017-12.1] - 2017-12-07
### Changed
- Fix drag and drop shift in coordinates.

## [2017-12.0] - 2017-12-01
### Added
- This ChangeLog.
- A shell script "jaamsim-linux.sh" to run JaamSim on Linux without crashing.

### Changed
- New user interface based on a single window containing internal sub-windows.
